::Feline::

She responded, "Right away commander."

She left her quarters and went to FZ's postition. "Yes Commander. Feline2 
reporting for duty." She put one hand on her hip and let the other one hang 
down.  Her tail was twitching slightly.  She had on a seductive smile and 
purred softly. "What is required of me?" she said in a soft voice.
